description: Harrogate ease relegation worries at the expense of fellow strugglers Tranmere
title: Harrogate Town 3-2 Tranmere Rovers
title_page: Harrogate Town 3-2 Tranmere Rovers: League Two - BBC Sport
maintext:
Harrogate Town have failed to win any of their nine Football League games against Tranmere Rovers (D3 L6), losing each of their last three in succession.
Tranmere Rovers have scored in each of their nine Football League games against Harrogate Town, scoring 17 goals in total across that time.
Harrogate are winless in their last eight midweek (Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday) league games (D2 L6) since winning their first such game of this season 2-0 over Doncaster in September.
No side has picked up fewer points away from home in League Two this season than Tranmere (13), although Rovers are unbeaten in their last three on the road (W1 D2).
